title: Comparison of Red Bull Racing SPECT Eyewear Goggles - Shelter, Buckler, Magnetron
description:
Shop for either Red Bull Racing Shelter Goggles, Buckler Goggles, or Magnetron Goggles at Abt: http://www.abt.com/brand/RedBullRacing?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=RedBullRacing_20160929

Red Bull Racing Shelter Goggle Features:

Half rim frame for slimlined look

Polyurethane frame and TR90 outrigger

Poly-carbonate spherical lens with anti-scratch treatment and UV protection

Cellulose Propionate (CP) inner lens for anti-fogging

Triple layer face foam

Double silicone line on the inside of the strap to ensure grip

Fits all helmets 

Red Bull SPECT vent system

Red Bull SPECT Shelter Goggles color options: red snow blue snow silver snow purple snow black snow

Red Bull Racing Buckler Goggle Features:

Polyurethane frame and TR90 outrigger

Poly-carbonate spherical lens with anti-scratch treatment and UV protection

Cellulose Propionate (CP) inner lens for anti-fogging

Triple layer face foam

Double silicone line on the inside of the strap to ensure grip

Fits all helmets

Red Bull SPECT vent system

Buckler Len Color Options: red snow blue snow silver snow purple snow black show

Red Bull Racing Magnetron Goggle Features:

Extra strong magnetic system for interchangeable lenses

Included 2nd lens for bad weather condition

Polyurethane frame

Poly-carbonate spherical lens with anti-scratch treatment and UV protection

Cellulose Propionate (CP) inner lens

Triple layer face foam

Double silicone line on the inside of the strap to ensure grip

Fits all helmets

Red Bull SPECT vent system

Red Bull Racing SPECT Eyewear Magnetron Goggles color options: silver snow blue snow red snow purple snow cloudy snow (2nd lens)
